-- GM says December U.S. sales fall 31 percent
-- 
-- Mon Jan 5, 2009 2:05pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/01/05/us-general-motors-sb-idUSTRE5044A420090105

 

 (Reuters) - General Motors Corp said December U.S. sales fell 31 percent from previous year. 

 * Reports 221,983 deliveries in December; 2,980,688 vehicles sold in 2008 * Says North America Q1 2009 production forecast at 420,000 vehicles * Says in December, GM North America produced 249,000 vehicles, down 1 percent